			<h4><a id="comment_link_64417" name="comment_link_64417" href="//use.perl.org/comments.pl?sid=40634&amp;cid=64417" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(64417)">META.yml repository HOWTO</a>
			
			<span id="comment_score_64417" class="score">(<a href="#" onclick="getModalPrefs('modcommentlog', 'Moderation Comment Log', 64417); return false">Score:1</a>)</span></h4>
		</div>
		<div class="details">
			by
			<a href="//use.perl.org/~grink/">grink (8549)</a>
			
			
			<span class="otherdetails" id="comment_otherdetails_64417"></span>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64417"><p>with Module::Install, add the following to your Makefile.PL:<br><code><br>resources repository =&gt; 'http://...';<br></code></p><p>with MakeMaker, add the following to WriteMakefile (thanks claes):<br><code><br>EXTRA_META =&gt; q{<br>resources:<br>
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; repository: <a href="http://.../" title="..." rel="nofollow">http://.../</a> [...]<br>},<br></code></p></div>
		
	
	</div>
	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_64417"></div>

</div>


